## The Threat of Power Starvation
In autonomous kinetic operations, an unmonitored power drop is as dangerous as a physical collision. If the supply voltage feeding the drive-by-wire system drops unexpectedly, the physical relays can fail in an unpredictable or "open" state, resulting in a runaway asset. Most commercial systems monitor battery life via a cloud API. If the connection drops, the system flies blind.

## The Localized Overwatch Daemon
Project Ebony completely severs the power management system from the cloud. We utilize portable Jackery micro-grids stationed directly at the asset's perimeter. 

To prevent power starvation from compromising the Kinetic Guillotine, we engineered the **Microgrid Power Matrix**.
